title: Grateful Dead Live at Club Melk Weg on 1981-10-16
description:
Set I
Acoustic Set

On The Road Again
Dire Wolf
Monkey & The Engineer
Bird Song
Cassidy
Oh Babe It Ain't No Lie
The Race is On
Ripple
Set II
Electric Set

Playing In The Band >
Hully Gully >
The Wheel >
Samson & Delilah
Gloria >
Turn On Your Lovelight >
Goin' Down The Road Feeling Bad >
Playing In The Band Reprise >
Black Peter >
Sugar Magnolia

 
Comment
Set I is Bobby and Jerry playing acoustic on borrowed instruments.

Cindy Poris opened
No encore performed

Jerry Garcia - Guitar
Bob Weir - Guitar
Brent Mydland - Keyboards
Phil Lesh - Bass
Bill Kreutzmann - Drums
Mickey Hart - Drums
